<h1>Welcome</h1>
<p>The B &amp; B World offers a wide range of bed and breakfasts in England, Wales, Scotland, Northern Ireland &amp; Ireland. Whether you are looking for an overnight stop for your business trip or you are looking to have a short break for the weekend we are the accommodation website to find it on.</p>

<p>You can contact the owners direct from their listing on our website. Each B &amp; B listing shows detailed descriptions and lists the accommodations features as well. You can also visit their website directly from us and any emails will go straight to the accommodation owner.</p>

<p>The B &amp; B World has a simple way to search, you can type in a location above to find your B &amp; B and you can also refine your search by clicking on the Search Options above. We are your comprehensive guide to B&B's in the UK and Ireland. </p>

<p>Get searching now to find your perfect B &amp; B on <a href="http://www.thebandbworld.co.uk/">thebandbworld.co.uk</a></p>


